COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 513, L.D. 806
1 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
2 number to read consecutively.
3 SUMMARY
44 This amendment provides that an expanded function dental assistant licensed by the
55 Board of Dental Practice is not required to be separately licensed as a radiographer by the
66 Radiologic Technology Board of Examiners. The amendment also adds an emergency
77 preamble and emergency clause to the bill.
